## Installation

```bash
pip install ghtraf
```

### From Source
```bash
git clone https://github.com/djdarcy/github-traffic-tracker.git
cd github-traffic-tracker
pip install -e .
```

### Manual Setup (no pip)
```bash
python setup-gists.py
```
